test_zero_range:
assert [0] == []
  Left contains one more item: 0
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [0]
  ?  +
test_large_range:
assert [1] == [4, 5, 6, 7, 8]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 4
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: 5
  Full diff:
  - [4, 5, 6, 7, 8]
  + [1]
test_even_range:
assert [2] == [8, 10, 12, 14, 16]
  At index 0 diff: 2 != 8
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: 10
  Full diff:
  - [8, 10, 12, 14, 16]
  + [2]
